2 Section 5. There is hereby appropriated General Fund moneys in the amount of
3 $25,000,000 in fiscal year 2026-2027 to the abandoned home pool fund.
4 Section 6. Whereas providing timely funding for housing assistance in the
5 Commonwealth is critically important for citizens of this state, an emergency is declared
6 to exist, and this Act takes effect July 1, 2026.
